Server.CourseInfo

Class CourseOffering

  • java.lang.Object
    • Server.CourseInfo.CourseOffering

  • public class CourseOffering
extends java.lang.Object
    This class deals with the course offering of course. It stores the section number, capacity and registrations of course.
    Author:
    Gurmukh Singh, Dillon Sahadevan, Eduardo Benetti
